snippet.title: 2017 Splatoon 2 World Inkling Invitational - Round Robin - Part 2 - Nintendo E3 2017
snippet.description:
Check out 2017 Splatoon 2 World Inkling Invitational - Round Robin - Part 2 at Nintendo E3 2017. 

The 2017 Splatoon 2 World Inkling Invitational features Splatoon 2 for Nintendo Switch. Composed of four pre-qualified squid squads from the U.S., Japan, Europe and Australia/New Zealand, the tournament finds teams participating in the first-ever international Splatoon 2 competition.

Splatoon 2 is Available July 21st! https://goo.gl/FJ9wFE
